  "title": "Operations Support Assistant (5 Months Contract)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Duration: Early Feb 2026 – End Jul 2026 (Maternity cover)</strong><br /><strong>\nSalary: $2,800 – $3,000</strong><br /><strong>\nLocation: Shenton Way</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Update records, databases, and documents.</li><li>Coordinate with the office, ships, suppliers, and contractors.</li><li>Assist with reports, audits, and company projects.</li><li>Handle purchase orders, invoices, mails, and courier deliveries.</li><li>Support the team with ad-hoc administrative tasks.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Accounting, Business Administration, Maritime, or related fields.</li><li>Training is provided.</li><li>Comfortable with Microsoft Office 365 (Excel, Word, PowerPoint, OneDrive).</li><li>Good with numbers and basic report analysis.</li><li>Team player with good communication skills and a positive attitude.</li></ul><p>Interested applicants, please email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:lilian@juhlerprofessionals.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">lilian@juhlerprofessionals.com.sg</a></p><p>Tan Li Lian</p><p>EA 01C3135</p><p>Reg R1100465</p>",
